UPDATE tts_models
SET
    is_public_listing_approved = ?,
    is_locked_from_user_modification = ?,
    is_locked_from_use = ?,
    maybe_mod_comments = ?,
    maybe_mod_user_token = ?,
    is_front_page_featured = ?,
    is_twitch_featured = ?,
    maybe_suggested_unique_bot_command = ?,
    use_default_mel_multiply_factor = ?,
    maybe_custom_mel_multiply_factor = ?,
    version = version + 1
WHERE token = ?
LIMIT 1
